name: CheckIn
text message: Sorry to hear that you are not having a good day. It is completely normal to be going through a difficult time now. Remember that you are not alone. Here is an activity that might also help...
name of flow: PLH - Content - Relax - CheckIn - List of things

name: CheckIn
text message:
Make a list of healthy activities that you like to do. Here are some suggestions:
• Listening to your favourite music
• Going for a walk (if allowed)
• Doing some exercise
• Drinking a cup of tea by yourself
• Calling up a friend
• Singing, dancing, praying, or reading
• Sitting in the sun with your eyes closed
• Watching your favourite T.V. show
Pick one and do it today!
name of flow: PLH - Content - Relax - CheckIn - List of things

name: CheckIn
text message: We hope that was helpful! Remember you can always type "Help" at anytime if you need an activity to help you relax or reduce stress. Chat to you later!
name of flow: PLH - Content - Relax - CheckIn - List of things
